          <div class="about_title">
            <p>Fei Wang</p>
          </div>
          <div class="about_container">
            <div class="about_brief">
              ​<span class="bold" id="about_link_1">Fei Wang</span> is a thinker, designer and runner based in sunny chilly San Francisco.

              <br>He currently serves as the curator of <span class="bold" id="about_link_2">Another Leap</span> exhibition at the Power Station of Art in Shanghai, as well as a researcher of <span class="bold" id="about_link_3">Taobao villages</span> with AliResearch of Alibaba.​ He leads<span class="bold" id="about_link_4"> Inside x Insight</span>, a data-driven media embeded in WeChat platform. ​

              <br>Fei enjoys re-imagining the role of designer in​ an age when "everybody and everything got wired". Since 2010, He has initiated and developed a series of <span class="bold" id="about_link_5">projects</span> that merge digital interfaces with data, analytics, urbanism, art, and fun. Working with multiple institutions and companies such as Alibaba, The New Museum, Power Station of Art and MTA of New York, Fei engages the public audience through​​ interactive design, data visualization, urban mapping and graphic story-telling.</br>
              Fei received Master of Architecture from Princeton University and ​graduated with History and Theory Prize (2014). Before coming to the US, he studied at Tsinghua University in Beijing and received his Bachelor and Master of Architecture with Distinction (2012). He was the recipient of 1st Prize of Autodesk Design Competition, <span class="bold" id="about_link_7">VELUX</span> Design Honor, <!--span class="bold" id="about_link_8">MAD Travel Fellowship</span> (2011),-->and the <span class="bold" id="about_link_9">inaugural fellow</span> of Emerging Curator Program at Power Station of Art Museum.</br>
              In his spare time, Fei runs and <span class="bold" id="about_link_10">photographs</span>. So far he has finished four <span class="bold" id="about_link_11">marathons</span>.<br></br>To enjoy this site's full content, beat GFW if applicable :)
            </div>
